  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149180/extras/b4f13a1cc0bedcf8e944a03c3b14c377.avif?t=1731469077\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this short and thrilling experience, join Thomas, a young explorer, and Lucy, a brave princess, on an adventure to restore order and peace between the demon, human, and fairy kingdoms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by classic RPG games, dive into a magical and captivating experience that will draw you into its world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note: This game is currently only available in Spanish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149180/extras/b4f13a1cc0bedcf8e944a03c3b14c377.avif?t=1731469077\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this short and thrilling experience, join Thomas, a young explorer, and Lucy, a brave princess, on an adventure to restore order and peace between the demon, human, and fairy kingdoms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by classic RPG games, dive into a magical and captivating experience that will draw you into its world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note: This game is currently only available in Spanish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
